[I] A fully featured GTK+ based wave viewer

[T] GTKWave is a fully featured GTK+ based wave viewerm which reads LXT,
[T] LXT2, VZT, FST, and GHW files as well as standard Verilog VCD/EVCD
[T] files and allows their viewing.

